claim.claim-text:
1. A device for holding articles comprising: 
a) a wire frame comprising: 
i) a paper receiving section having a set of compression points to allow paper to be fit snugly therein; 
ii) a visor receiving section having a set of compression points to allow a visor to be fit snugly therein; 

b) a clip coupled to said wire frame, said clip having a compression point, to allow a pair of glasses to be fit snugly therein.
